{"tid":1572330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<深入反思>香港平行時空","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:41:42.000Z","uid":164008,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"777da17b4a76cc293edae7251b5012c6d331fa98","tid":1572330,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的 開場白 首先多謝手足們 勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但想喺臨訓前俾大家一個認真思考<br />\n<br />\n今日 小弟專登無跟大隊<br />\n<br />\n無上連登 嘗試走出同溫層<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果發現 同溫層嘅可怕 香港嘅平行時空<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNUOqKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNUOqKL.jpg&h=f3e4b25a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖以證今日 希慎開始關門 <br />\n<br />\n就喺銅鑼灣開始多手足聚集<br />\n<br />\n其實內街見更多嘅 係純粹出後行街<br />\n<br />\n享受一般星期日嘅市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而之後由中央圖書館 到砲台山 北角<br />\n<br />\n嗰種風平浪靜 完全唔似另一邊有社運<br />\n<br />\n到6點返到九龍旺角 7點元朗 完全係<br />\n<br />\n平行時空 <br />\n<br />\n好難想像 到7點北角出防暴 跟住勇武私了<br />\n<br />\n小弟身邊至少有2/3和理非無出席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到底 並非想放負<br />\n<br />\n但好多淺黃其實都慢慢回歸正常生活<br />\n<br />\n係文宣唔夠?定運動難以持續?<br />\n<br />\n今日私了可能制裁咗藍絲暴徒<br />\n<br />\n但始終係政府成功以民打民<br />\n<br />\n對黑警 始終無能為力 手足被捕 春袋仍在<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以重點 我哋嘅終極升級到底幾時?<br />\n<br />\n會係咩? 對黑警能否跨越只守不攻嘅<br />\n<br />\n道德界線?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要不集中營 要不煲底<br />\n<br />\n要記住 我哋仲未打贏場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efa9af7f1a48a573f2c87d70ddf70aacaaa2bcf","tid":1572330,"uid":164008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be848ed7bc85cffc2e91d3eabd1c3c4613e23cf","tid":1572330,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044704e9d1812ecf8d019e8d75fc52ba4106addf","tid":1572330,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"應該係避免唔到<br />\n即使198x 年韓國<br />\n應該都有好多韓豬我估"},{"pid":"2ff2ea3d77f46589a64551c4e71e40b4f773f717","tid":1572330,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"posh"},{"pid":"22b4b72ca5cef8afa1ad5c8fb14876d20ab542bf","tid":1572330,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"你啲圖呢？"},{"pid":"b5314fb419b39af30500e61ffb800c219df63ba3","tid":1572330,"uid":164008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"離開大隊就會見到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尤其一家大細 <br />\n<br />\n40歲以上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比當初100萬 200萬+1<br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅參與性低唔少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺砲台山站見到2位手足4點貼文宣<br />\n<br />\n講真嗰刻佢哋被人溶咗都無人知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以10月1號會唔會係終極死線<br />\n<br />\n到時一樣對黑警 仲係哋be water又等新一日?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我所期望嘅係 可以推動到出翻200萬人<br />\n<br />\n對準政權 終極升級 不撤不散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d40df01c9cfcafed7847dc48f1500f85a5a8e51","tid":1572330,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"［極重要］全民錫春袋！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b3682bfecf3ea2f8bdafa04195c4ddaf73747a7","tid":1572330,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sh1UmqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSh1UmqT.jpg&h=ceecfdca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oD1tqSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo